steps.description:
For a 3 lb (1.4 kg) roast, sprinkle about 1.5 tsp (7.5 g) of this blend evenly on all sides and massage it in gently with your fingers. Then, continue with your recipe as instructed. For instance, your recipe may advise you to:
season the beef;
tie it with cooking twine at 3 in (7.6 cm) intervals to give it a cylindrical shape;
use a roasting pan to cook it in a 375 °F (191 °C) oven;
remove it when the beef's internal temperature reads 140 °F (60 °C);
cover the roast with foil and let it rest for 10 minutes before serving.
